                    </div>

                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
                        <div class="steps">
                            <h3>Vision</h3>
                            <p>Becoming a respectable software training and service provider creating opportunities for each and every stakeholder .</p>
                            <i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o"></i>
