                    </div>

                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
                        <div class="steps">
                            <h3>Values</h3>
                            <p>we believe in the following values -</p>
                            <ul class="bullet">
                                <li>Quality</li>
                                <li>Cost Effective</li>
                                <li>Integrity</li>
                                <li>Teamwork</li>
                                <li>Socially Responsible</li>
                            </ul>
